                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 10.77,
                                "byte_start": 92318,
                                "byte_stop": 135472,
                                "text": "Justice Blackmun will deliver the opinion for the Court in No. 81-1370, Energy Reserves Group versus Kansas Power \u0026 Light Company."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.77,
                        "stop": 135.003,
                        "byte_start": 135472,
                        "byte_stop": 632426,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15045,
                            "name": "Harry A. Blackmun",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/harry_a_blackmun",
                            "last_name": "Blackmun",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2689,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": 13755600,
                                    "date_end": 775890000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Richard Nixon",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2689"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32712,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 50281,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/harry_a_blackmun.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8821,
                            "identifier": "harry_a_blackmun"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 10.77,
                                "stop": 17.958,
                                "byte_start": 135472,
                                "byte_stop": 164207,
                                "text": "This case comes to us by way of an appeal from the Supreme Court of Kansas."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 17.958,
                                "stop": 23.578,
                                "byte_start": 164207,
                                "byte_stop": 186672,
                                "text": "It doesn\u0027t lend itself very well to a description from the bench."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 23.578,
                                "stop": 37.148,
                                "byte_start": 186672,
                                "byte_stop": 241007,
                                "text": "I think it will suffice to say that the case concerns intrastate gas contracts between the respective predecessors of the appellant producer and the appellee public utility."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 37.148,
                                "stop": 60.47,
                                "byte_start": 241007,
                                "byte_stop": 334212,
                                "text": "That these contracts contained an escalator clause and a price redetermination clause, and that the Federal Natural Gas Policy Act was in -- enacted in 1978 and replaced earlier federal price controls for interstate gas as well as extending federal price regulation to the intrastate gas market."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 60.47,
                                "stop": 74.427,
                                "byte_start": 334212,
                                "byte_stop": 390114,
                                "text": "And that a Kansas Act was enacted in May 1979 and imposed price controls on the intrastate market with respect to contracts executed before April 20, 1977."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 74.427,
                                "stop": 89.264,
                                "byte_start": 390114,
                                "byte_stop": 449464,
                                "text": "And that the parties are in dispute as to whether the new federal Act triggered the escalator clauses and enabled the producers when the utility refused to go along with a higher rate to terminate the contracts."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 89.264,
                                "stop": 102.894,
                                "byte_start": 449464,
                                "byte_stop": 503903,
                                "text": "In this litigation, a Kansas trial court entered summary judgment for the utility holding that the federal Act\u0027s imposition of price ceilings on intrastate gas did not trigger the governmental price escalator clauses."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 102.894,
                                "stop": 108.469,
                                "byte_start": 503903,
                                "byte_stop": 526264,
                                "text": "And that the Kansas Act did not violate the Contract Clause of the Federal Constitution."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 108.469,
                                "stop": 112.051,
                                "byte_start": 526264,
                                "byte_stop": 540579,
                                "text": "That reading was affirmed by the Supreme Court of Kansas."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 112.051,
                                "stop": 119.514,
                                "byte_start": 540579,
                                "byte_stop": 570463,
                                "text": "In an opinion filed today with the clerk, we in turn affirm the judgment of the Supreme Court of Kansas."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 119.514,
                                "stop": 135.003,
                                "byte_start": 570463,
                                "byte_stop": 632426,
                                "text": "Justice Powell has filed a separate opinion which joins the Court\u0027s opinion and except as to Part II-C and he is joined in that opinion by the Chief Justice and by Justice Rehnquist."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
